{"tid":1919134,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"曼聯準備賣連格？","createTime":"2020-03-10T14:43:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-11T03:13:15.000Z","uid":16659,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"8d620511c04d40fe9b6e3309df098152e2c5d244","tid":1919134,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T14:43:20.000Z","msg":"據Goal了解，曼聯領隊蘇斯克查對連格失去信心，球隊很大機會今夏賣走該前鋒。<br />\n<br />\n自波基斯費南迪斯1月加盟，加上恩哈路被借過來，連格在主要賽事上陣的機會更少。這位27歲前鋒合約到2021年屆滿，暫時還未有消息指球會想跟他續約。另外，此子亦找來在歐洲球壇人脈深廣的Mino Raiolaz作經紀，如果球季餘下時間情況還未有好轉，相信連格離隊可能性甚高。(<a href=\"http://Goal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FGoal.com&d=Pl33APIo1S6IjQ3qGLZsPXljxErbpFF6VcGzQu2DuOQ%3D&h=3b641610\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Goal.com</a>)"},{"pid":"f49f9335084b9be8a9ec0a50e951b463975a3dad","tid":1919134,"uid":54524,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T14:46:23.000Z","msg":"踢諾域治都冇位啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1eb2a60372cdb04f1017e5046706bbc42c3f629d","tid":1919134,"uid":23988,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T14:47:37.000Z","msg":"邊個會接垃圾咁傻仔"},{"pid":"14b03b175452a6e9b1546b2dbe744a3488575ae8","tid":1919134,"uid":34293,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T14:53:39.000Z","msg":"球場小醜"},{"pid":"609cf15fe3c76806cfbe40a249994ece8b6a1eb0","tid":1919134,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T14:57:02.000Z","msg":"叔叔不行了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ed30df9479ec340a11d4a73e999910d734565f1","tid":1919134,"uid":9435,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"1eb2a60372cdb04f1017e5046706bbc42c3f629d","tid":1919134,"uid":23988,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T14:47:37.000Z","msg":"邊個會接垃圾咁傻仔"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T14:58:50.000Z","msg":"國米"},{"pid":"fab697e2253be0392cdd52f390e46321eee97673","tid":1919134,"ui